      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid option for someone needing a dependable commuter. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a few small dings around the door panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some light staining from years of use. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it lacks the refinement of a newer model. It is a functional, honest car that has been maintained to remain roadworthy despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
