    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the iconic S54 3.2L high-revving straight-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual. The VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring optimal variable valve timing. It retains its factory limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing upgraded bushings to sharpen turn-in response. A driver-focused example that prioritizes mechanical feedback and analog engagement.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
