    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers the perfect balance of luxury and performance. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor signs of careful road use consistent with its history. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of major blemishes, while every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been serviced with precision, providing a smooth, responsive drive and firm handling that inspires confidence. It has been garage-kept and smoke-free, representing a reliable, elegant choice for a discerning driver who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
