    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six engineering. The powerplant features individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated Double-VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the rev range. Power is managed by a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for precise corner-exit traction. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary stress points. Equipped with a refreshed suspension featuring upgraded bushings and staggered alloys, this M3 offers the mechanical feedback and lateral composure expected of a legitimate driver's tool. It presents in honest condition, prioritized for those who value drivetrain integrity and kinematic precision.",
